{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"CSS セレクターと XPath の比較","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Comparison_with_CSS_selectors","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div style=\"background:#f5f5f5; margin: 5px 0;\" id=\"sect1\">\n    <b><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XSLT/Transforming_XML_with_XSLT/The_Netscape_XSLT_XPath_Reference\">XSLT/XPath リファレンス</a></b>: <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XSLT/Element\">XSLT 要素</a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/EXSLT\">EXSLT 関数</a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Functions\">XPath 関数</a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Axes\">XPath 軸</a>\n</div>{{Page(\"/ja/docs/Web/XPath\", \"Subnav\")}}<p></p>\n\n<p class=\"summary\">この記事では、Web 開発者が適切な仕事に適切なツールをよりよく選択できるように、 CSS セレクタと XPath の違いを文書化して Web 開発者に提供しています。</p>\n\n<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XPath\">XPath 機能</a></th>\n   <th scope=\"col\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Selectors\">相当する CSS</a></th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Axes/ancestor\"><code>ancestor</code></a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Axes/parent\"><code>parent</code></a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Axes/preceding-sibling\"><code>preceding-sibling</code></a> 軸</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS/:has\"><code>:has()</code></a> セレクター <svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Axes/attribute\"><code>attribute</code></a> 軸</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS/Attribute_selectors\">属性セレクター</a></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Axes/child\"><code>child</code></a> 軸</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS/Child_combinator\">子結合子</a></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Axes/descendant\"><code>descendant</code></a